summary:
So far I really like it. Slightly regretting getting one without the paddle shifters, but it drives really well anyway. Very tight handling. Plenty of power. Looks GREAT.
I wish the 2017 had Apple CarPlay, but I’ll survive just fine without it.
Oh, and I wish there was a way to disable stop/start permanently, rather than having to toggle it off every time I get in the car.
